 *   Grouped by version in the UI (Google Play release-notes style). 10 unique post-versions →
 *   10 release cards. De-dup rules applied: each storeDescription line appears exactly once
 *   across all versions. v1.8, v1.9, v1.11, v1.12, v1.14 have posts but no storeDescription
 *   (all lines were covered by earlier versions or by feature posts in the same group).
